data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath home completely re-done. Interior replaced down to the studs, new roof and new HVAC. Inviting open concept living, dining, and kitchen with a split bedroom plan. Exterior boasts a completely fenced 0.45 acre lot with ample room to park a boat or RV. A large +/-600 SF storage building, and a 50 amp RV hookup are included. Located on a quiet street not far from the community pool, park, boat ramp, and fishing pier in Holiday Beach. An ideal place for your forever or vacation coastal home.
